text: Pengkalan Batu or Pangkalan Batu may refer to: == Brunei == * Kampong Pengkalan Batu, village in Brunei-Muara District * Pengkalan Batu, Brunei- Muara, mukim (subdistrict) of Brunei-Muara District == Malaysia == * Pengkalan Batu (state constituency), state constituency in Malacca
title: Pengkalan Batu
